\SE[56] I'm sorry... Laura. \SE[42] I... I can no longer be
by your side...

\SE[4]Huh... Huh...!? \SE[14]You're going to the school...?
\SE[57]Just for five years...! I... I won't be...!!

I already told you, didn't I? We are 'Alice.' The 'Alice' of
'Knowledge' and 'Destruction'.

\SE[0]Um, you see... We thought that since you looked a
little pitiful when we took away your mom... \SE[0]We wanted
to let you meet her one last time!

\SE[5]Yes, it's over now. \SE[1]Good job up until here...
Laura- chan? \SE[23]Thank you for bringing Mom with you.
Thank you.
\SE[]Lunaroa? \!\SE[]What do you think about this flower?

\SE Right?! \SE With this, we can make the perfect Flower
Crown!

\SE[]Um, um...? I, um... \SE[]I have something I want to ask
Lunaroa...
\SE Um, um...? Well... \SE When we grow up...
\SE[]\SM[double]Sure! I want to marry Laura too!

\SE[]But my dad said that you can only get married if it's
between a man and a woman...

\SE[]I heard from the traveling poet! \.In a country called
Yurishin, girls can get married to each other now!

\SE[]Is that so? Then it's okay! \!\SE[]\SM[nod]Yes! I will
marry Laura!

\SE[]\SM[pop]Yay! So, which one of us will be the bride?
\!\SE[]Luna, which one do you prefer?

\SE[]Laura can choose! \!\SE[]...Ah! How about the taller
one becomes the bride and the smaller one becomes the wife?
\SE[]Oh no...! What if I don't grow at all...?

\SE[]I'm sorry... Laura. \SE[]I might not be able to stay by
your side anymore...

\SE[]Huh... Huh...!? \SE[]You're going to school...?
\SE[]Just for about five years...! I... I'm not... at all!!

I already told you, didn't I? We are 'Alice'. The 'Alice' of
'Knowledge' and 'Destruction'.

\SE[]Um, you see... \!\SE[]We thought that if we took away
your mom, you would be a little bit sad... \!\SE[]So we
decided to let you meet her one last time!

\SE Yes, it's over now. \SE Thank you for bringing Mom here,
Laura-chan. \SE Thank you for everything you've done.
